{"tid":2019791,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街屋企人（想聽下大家故事）","createTime":"2020-05-16T14:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T15:10:26.000Z","uid":157321,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b5f8ad20c504ada82dfe1ad06192fbb99452c548","tid":2019791,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\">屋企有個仆街老豆，從小就偏心屋企細個個，對我似狗一樣。啊媽以前會為我打抱不平，稍為同佢嘈兩句，宜家我老豆極過份既嘢都做得出，但佢竟然叫我忍佢，佢為咗頭家唔好散寧願犧牲我，由我抑鬱受折磨。有時諗自己做錯乜嘢，見到人地開心家庭好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知有無巴絲屋企仲衰過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我唔洗怨天由人 覺得上帝都懶理我死活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></div></div>"},{"pid":"17c5b9396e9aa4162e1e205ca34cf4de44b64978","tid":2019791,"uid":171451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:12:03.000Z","msg":"有無能力搬出去？<br />\n抑鬱有無搵人幫？<br />\n自己救自己呀"},{"pid":"ae8de6a8dde913ca52007d8ed68c740b6965693b","tid":2019791,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c5b9396e9aa4162e1e205ca34cf4de44b64978","tid":2019791,"uid":171451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:12:03.000Z","msg":"有無能力搬出去？<br />\n抑鬱有無搵人幫？<br />\n自己救自己呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:36:42.000Z","msg":"本身有外地伴侶 已經計劃好曬走 但武肺搞到市又唔好無工開又唔知等幾多年先走到 我都好想自救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5731c5910321e2cb43ada91a54af7123f04f8aad","tid":2019791,"uid":155725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:39:52.000Z","msg":"有個仆街老豆<br />\n我都已經唔期望會得到家庭溫暖，<br />\n唔洗錫我，唔好控制我同要求我跟佢嗰套就得。不嬲都<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，已經準備搬走了，<br />\n所以佢有咩問題都唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fa3b16636e30a78890ed2b02340ff5cc38963c","tid":2019791,"uid"