得鬧鳩我 <br />\n最好笑係個老豆怕老婆到粒聲都唔出就唒佢<br />\n我係呢個屋企已經感覺唔到開心 晚晚都自己係房喊 最近有d好開心嘅消息 但係一諗起又係要比個老母管撚住 我真係笑唔出<br />\n呢一刻仲讀緊書要靠屋企先冇得走<br />\n好彩有個好好嘅男朋友 為左我好努力番工揾錢想帶我離開呢個惡夢嘅地方"},{"pid":"e4fbe906e996b55d32382044cabb26a5d0416db8","tid":2019791,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61ad107b8ba121aee5c4f233cde94b8e8628ab3e","tid":2019791,"uid":234788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5f8ad20c504ada82dfe1ad06192fbb99452c548","tid":2019791,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\">屋企有個仆街老豆，從小就偏心屋企細個個，對我似狗一樣。啊媽以前會為我打抱不平，稍為同佢嘈兩句，宜家我老豆極過份既嘢都做得出，但佢竟然叫我忍佢，佢為咗頭家唔好散寧願犧牲我，由我抑鬱受折磨。有時諗自己做錯乜嘢，見到人地開心家庭好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知有無巴絲屋企仲衰過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我唔洗怨天由人 覺得上帝都懶理我死活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></div></div>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"當屋企都唔係一個可以放鬆既地方，<br />\n其實真係唔知去邊到有個安身之所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打已經出黎社會工作？阿爸仲有D咩可以操控住你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"係 但武肺失業 想走都走唔到 身邊朋友叫我忍 沙士都6月完 武肺都唔會完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心灰到想自殺試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b87728da180e457bc34a42bc6bc1cccece3d77","tid":2019791,"uid":157321,"like":0,"disl